itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway watch the SpaceX Rocket Launch live up until the cancellation but the show must go on! They ponder how astronauts use the bathroom while they are wearing their space suits, debate whether or not 2020 could get any worse, and why Robert Rodriguez won’t let Ross direct the next “Machete”.
